textBoxes.content: But at that moment he looked scared and small I hated what they turned him into.
I was the tax collector, and not just any tax collector, it was a custom-house offical. they were the worst and most hated.
And they were going to reap whaat they sowed.
I was watching. I saw everything and I never forgot.
That was the moment I decided I was never going to be like my Father
